      sparkle:edSignature attribute is computed by `sign_update`
      (third_party/sparkle/bin/sign_update <artifact>) using your
      private key from the keychain.

    <item>
      <title>Version 0.5.1</title>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>0.5.1</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.5.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
        https://github.com/msgbyte/dao-browser/releases/tag/v0.5.1
      </sparkle:releaseNotesLink>
      <enclosure
        url="https://github.com/msgbyte/dao-browser/releases/download/v0.5.1/dao-browser-0.5.1-mac-arm64.dmg"
        sparkle:edSignature="REPLACE_WITH_SIGN_UPDATE_OUTPUT"
        length="123456789"
        type="application/octet-stream" />
    </item>
    -->
        <item>
